{
  "data": {
    "attributes": {
      "npcId": 1013000,
      "questId": 22507,
      "questName": "Spirit Pact",
      "startStateMachine": {
        "startState": "mirSpeaks1",
        "states": [
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
                {
                  "nextState": "playerResponse1",
                  "text": "Next"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendNext",
              "text": "I knew it! I knew we were connected, master! When you get stronger, I get stronger, too. And when I get stronger, you can use my strength! That's our pact. I knew I picked a good master!"
            },
            "id": "mirSpeaks1",
            "type": "dialogue"
          },
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
                {
                  "nextState": "mirSpeaks1",
                  "text": "Previous"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": "mirSpeaks2",
                  "text": "Next"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendNextPrev",
              "speaker": "CHARACTER",
              "text": "#bI see. How did we end up in this pact anyway?"
            },
            "id": "playerResponse1",
            "type": "dialogue"
          },
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
                {
                  "nextState": "playerResponse1",
                  "text": "Previous"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": "playerResponse2",
                  "text": "Next"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendNextPrev",
              "text": "I don't know. I was just an egg. I can't really remember...though I faintly recall you, master, walking toward me in a foggy forest. I remember your surprise upon seeing me. And I was calling out to you in return."
            },
            "id": "mirSpeaks2",
            "type": "dialogue"
          },
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
                {
                  "nextState": "mirSpeaks2",
                  "text": "Previous"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": "mirSpeaks3",
                  "text": "Next"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendNextPrev",
              "speaker": "CHARACTER",
              "text": "#b#b(Wait! That sounds just like that one dream you had... Did the two of you meet in a dream? Is it possible that the giant Dragon you saw in that dream was...#p1013000#?)"
            },
            "id": "playerResponse2",
            "type": "dialogue"
          },
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
                {
                  "nextState": "playerResponse2",
                  "text": "Previous"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": "playerResponse3",
                  "text": "Next"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendNextPrev",
              "text": "Master, you and I are one in spirit. I knew it the moment I saw you. That's why I wanted to make the pact with you. No one else. You had to pay the price I set, of course."
            },
            "id": "mirSpeaks3",
            "type": "dialogue"
          },
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
                {
                  "nextState": "mirSpeaks3",
                  "text": "Previous"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": "mirSpeaks4",
                  "text": "Next"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendNextPrev",
              "speaker": "CHARACTER",
              "text": "#bI paid a price?"
            },
            "id": "playerResponse3",
            "type": "dialogue"
          },
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
                {
                  "nextState": "playerResponse3",
                  "text": "Previous"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": "playerResponse4",
                  "text": "Next"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendNextPrev",
              "text": "Don't you remember? When you recognized me and touched me? That was the one condition I set. The moment you touched my egg, you and I became one in spirit."
            },
            "id": "mirSpeaks4",
            "type": "dialogue"
          },
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
                {
                  "nextState": "mirSpeaks4",
                  "text": "Previous"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": "mirSpeaks5",
                  "text": "Next"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendNextPrev",
              "speaker": "CHARACTER",
              "text": "#bOne in...spirit?"
            },
            "id": "playerResponse4",
            "type": "dialogue"
          },
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
                {
                  "nextState": "playerResponse4",
                  "text": "Previous"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": "playerResponse5",
                  "text": "Next"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendNextPrev",
              "text": "Yes! The Spirit Pact! You and I have seperate bodies, but we share one spirit. That's why you get stronger when I get stronger, and vice versa! Awesome, right? At least, I think so."
            },
            "id": "mirSpeaks5",
            "type": "dialogue"
          },
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
                {
                  "nextState": "mirSpeaks5",
                  "text": "Previous"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": "mirSpeaks6",
                  "text": "Next"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendNextPrev",
              "speaker": "CHARACTER",
              "text": "#bI have no idea what you're talking about, but it sounds like a pretty big deal."
            },
            "id": "playerResponse5",
            "type": "dialogue"
          },
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
                {
                  "nextState": "playerResponse5",
                  "text": "Previous"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": "playerResponse6",
                  "text": "Next"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendNextPrev",
              "text": "Of course it's a big deal, silly master! You never have to worry about monsters again. You have me to protect you now! Go ahead and test me. In fact, let's go right now!"
            },
            "id": "mirSpeaks6",
            "type": "dialogue"
          },
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
                {
                  "nextState": "mirSpeaks6",
                  "text": "Previous"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": "mirSpeaks7",
                  "text": "Next"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendNextPrev",
              "speaker": "CHARACTER",
              "text": "#bBut it's peaceful here. There are no dangerous monsters around."
            },
            "id": "playerResponse6",
            "type": "dialogue"
          },
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
                {
                  "nextState": "playerResponse6",
                  "text": "Previous"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": "playerResponse7",
                  "text": "Next"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendNextPrev",
              "text": "WHAT?! That's no fun! Don't you like adventuring, master? Fighting monsters on behalf of your people, defeating evil, rescuing the innocent, and all that? You're not into that kind of thing?"
            },
            "id": "mirSpeaks7",
            "type": "dialogue"
          },
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
                {
                  "nextState": "mirSpeaks7",
                  "text": "Previous"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": "acceptPact",
                  "text": "Next"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendNextPrev",
              "speaker": "CHARACTER",
              "text": "#bIt's not part of my five year plan. I'm just kidding, but seriously, I'm a farmer's kid..."
            },
            "id": "playerResponse7",
            "type": "dialogue"
          },
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
                {
                  "nextState": "completeQuest",
                  "text": "Accept"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": "declined",
                  "text": "Decline"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendAcceptDecline",
              "text": "Bah, well let me tell you this. It's impossible for a Dragon Master to live a peaceful life. I'll have plenty of chances to prove my skills. Trust me, our life will be one big adventure. Promise me that you'll stick with me, okay?\r\n\r\n#fUI/UIWindow.img/QuestIcon/8/0# 810 exp"
            },
            "id": "acceptPact",
            "type": "dialogue"
          },
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
                {
